&lt;p&gt;Applications are invited for the above post in the Department of Neuropathology at the John Radcliffe Hospital, Oxford.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are aiming to recruit a motivated, committed, and flexibly minded NHS neuropathology consultant to join our neuropathology team. Our priority is to appoint an individual, who is able to provide cover for all aspects of the service as part of the consultant team (neurosurgical, neuromuscular and general post-mortem work). In addition, a specific requirement for the post will be for the appointee to have an interest and basic experience in developmental / perinatal neuropathology and ophthalmic pathology&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;NameDr Monika HoferJob titleClinical Lead, Consultant NeuropathologistEmail addressmonika.hofer@ouh.nhs.ukTelephone number01865234904Additional contact information&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Candidates are encouraged to visit the department if possible and are invited to contact Dr Monika Hofer, Lead Consultant in Neuropathology (monika.hofer@ouh.nhs.uk) and Dr Ursula Schulz, Clinical Director for Neurosciences (Ursula.Schulz@ouh.nhs.uk).&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
